Package com.L3MON4D3.voc5.UI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EditActivity
    Editactivity is used to edit individual vocabularies It is started from the Gallery and receives and the vocabulary that should be edited in the intent with the key "com.L3MON4D3.voc5.Voc".
    GalleryActivity
    Displays all Vocabs and serves as a gateway to all main functions of the App.
    GalleryCard
    A Card that is used in GalleryActivity and displays Information on one Vocab.
    GalleryCardFactory
    Used to instanciate GalleryCards either with or without Actions.
    LernActivity
    LernActivity is used to query the individual words that are passed in an ArrayList.
    LoadingInfoActivity
    Provides functionality to display a loading-Animation to subclasses.
    LoginActivity
    Entry Point into App.
    Pop
    Pop checks the user response.
    VocActivity
    This class serves as a superclass for Classes that require a client.
